      "repository": "gordolio/Trio",
      "number": 1225,
      "title": "APSManager thread safety fixes (Part 1)",
      "body": "This will be the first of at least 3 Pull requests targeted at optimizing the thread safety of the APSManager. As suggested by @kingst in PR #1145 I splitted my initial PR in several smaller PRs to be able to better review the changes made.\r\n\r\nChanges made in this PR:\r\n\r\n- remove unused `viewContext`\r\n- move `tir()` out of a nested perform closure\r\n- add `[weak self]` to combine sinks and `privateContext` perform closures\r\n- move combine operations to receive on the main thread to avoid race conditions\r\n- remove force unwraps",
